Chelsea Fan Club SA – Website Development Project
Student: Wayrren Kerspuy
Student Number: ST10482500
Subject: WEBDE5020
Lecturer: Mr. R.Kobeni
~ Project Overview

The Chelsea Fan Club SA website is a multi-page fan platform designed to provide South African Chelsea supporters with club news, player profiles, images, contact options, and general community interaction.

The project was developed across three parts following course requirements:

Part 1: HTML structure, page creation, content research, and sitemap.

Part 2: Full CSS styling, layout, branding, mobile responsiveness, and improved design.

Part 3: JavaScript functionality, form validation, SEO implementation, improved interactivity, animations, maps, search features, and advanced UI behaviour.

This README contains the project documentation, changelog, technical overview, and references used throughout the assignment.

